      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing dependable daily transportation. The exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several visible scratches, some minor door dings, and a bit of paint fading on the hood. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and some staining on the carpets. While it isn't a show car, it has been mechanically maintained to ensure it remains roadworthy and consistent for its next owner.",
